config BR2_PACKAGE_PARKINSOUND_STEPGATE4
	bool "parkinsound-stepgate4"
	help
	  Parkinsound Step Gate 4 - a 4-channel 16-step audio gate
	  sequencer LV2 plugin for MOD devices.

	  Four independent mono voices share a single plug-in instance so
	  their step clocks are locked together sample-for-sample. The
	  Sync Source (Host Sync / Free Run) and Tempo are common to all
	  four channels, while each channel has its own rhythmic Division,
	  16 step On/Tie toggles and ADSR envelope. Because every voice is
	  advanced from one shared master beat, the four sequences trigger
	  simultaneously and never drift apart - solving the cross-plugin
	  synchronisation weakness of running several separate gate plugins
	  under mod-host / mod-ui.

	  https://github.com/pilali/Parkinsound
